  "activation": "$ultracode only",
  "notes": "PACKAGE_MANIFEST.json excludes itself from the file hash list.",
  "primary_changes": [
    "Codex-only layout: skill installs to .codex/skills/ultracode (verified Codex reads it); nothing is written to .agents/.",
    "Install overwrites in place with NO .bak backups; hook install replaces ultracode groups idempotently while preserving unrelated hooks.",
    "Hook router output matches Codex's embedded hook-output JSON schema (hookSpecificOutput wrapper; validated against the 0.136 binary schema).",
    "Profile is a standalone $CODEX_HOME/<name>.config.toml; legacy [profiles.X] removed.",
    "Real bug fixes (uc_verify shlex, uc_merge_results, adversarial subprocess timeout); gates ingest worker content; Stop hook checks artifacts+gate with an escape valve; quote-aware destructive-command detection; agents drift check; spawn-prompt role-instruction fallback.",
    "Cross-platform uninstall (--uninstall, project scope, Windows .ps1) prunes ultracode hook groups."
  ],
